com.psddev.dari.util

Class CloudStorageItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.util.AbstractStorageItem
      • com.psddev.dari.util.CloudStorageItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SettingsBackedObject, StorageItem

    public class CloudStorageItem
extends AbstractStorageItem
    StorageItem stored in the cloud.

    To use this class, it must be able to access the jclouds library. If you use Maven, you should add the following dependency:

    <dependency>
    <groupId>org.jclouds</groupId>
    <artifactId>jclouds-all</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.1</version>
</dependency>
